{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/Hear-Een-app-voor-doven/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Dit project heb ik gedaan in opdracht van <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ProjectBchallenge/?hc_ref=ARSAqWZGc9eopjGYsmf99T1Fl23ytFU-iiQv11y9MEQ__MNdiwsQ-pMx8PLIZDqWsjk&#x26;fref=nf\">Project B</a> van het bedrijf <a href=\"https://www.sogeti.nl/over-sogeti\">Sogeti</a>, een onderdeel van <a href=\"https://www.capgemini.com/nl-nl/\">Capgemini</a>. </p>\n<iframe width=\"854\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pLZORE6hHBc\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p>Het project stond ook onder de naam <em>Emerging technolgies</em>, met als doel om een product te bouwen voor mensen met een beperking. </p>\n<p>Wij hadden gekozen voor mensen met een auditieve beperking, dus doven en slechthorenden. Als product hebben we een app gemaakt, de app had de volgende features: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Spraak-naar-tekst</li>\n<li>Tekst-naar-Spraak</li>\n<li>Gebarenherkenning</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/297Hacker/Emerging_Technology78/\">Source Code</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/297Hacker/Emerging_Technology78/releases/download/v0.9-beta/hear.apk\">Download Link</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bedb98fc5b428a56d4b8e9442ce02255/302a4/apphear.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 177.91411042944785%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"App hear APK\"\n        title=\"App hear APK\"\n        src=\"/static/bedb98fc5b428a56d4b8e9442ce02255/a6d36/apphear.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bedb98fc5b428a56d4b8e9442ce02255/222b7/apphear.png 163w,\n/static/bedb98fc5b428a56d4b8e9442ce02255/ff46a/apphear.png 325w,\n/static/bedb98fc5b428a56d4b8e9442ce02255/a6d36/apphear.png 650w,\n/static/bedb98fc5b428a56d4b8e9442ce02255/e548f/apphear.png 975w,\n/static/bedb98fc5b428a56d4b8e9442ce02255/302a4/apphear.png 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>Gebarenherkenning</h1>\n<p>Gebarenherkenning was één van de moeilijkste features, deze is ook alleen maar gedeeltelijk uitgewerkt door middel van een Tensorflow machine learning algoritme. <a href=\"https://github.com/Steven24K/Sign-language-dataset\">Kijk op mijn GiTHub voor meer info</a>. Het is de basis voor image recognition, gemaakt met behulp van deze <a href=\"https://www.tensorflow.org/tutorials/image_recognition\">tutorial</a>.</p>\n<p>We hebben hier heel veel foto's van handgebaren gemaakt om een algoritme te trainen: </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0efbbdd38c76ce84b18fcdab79dd84f3/00602/drie-gebaar.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.852760736196316%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gebaren dataset\"\n        title=\"gebaren dataset\"\n        src=\"/static/0efbbdd38c76ce84b18fcdab79dd84f3/a6d36/drie-gebaar.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0efbbdd38c76ce84b18fcdab79dd84f3/222b7/drie-gebaar.png 163w,\n/static/0efbbdd38c76ce84b18fcdab79dd84f3/ff46a/drie-gebaar.png 325w,\n/static/0efbbdd38c76ce84b18fcdab79dd84f3/a6d36/drie-gebaar.png 650w,\n/static/0efbbdd38c76ce84b18fcdab79dd84f3/e548f/drie-gebaar.png 975w,\n/static/0efbbdd38c76ce84b18fcdab79dd84f3/3c492/drie-gebaar.png 1300w,\n/static/0efbbdd38c76ce84b18fcdab79dd84f3/00602/drie-gebaar.png 1671w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Die vervolgens te labelen door alles in mapjes te zetten, beginnend met de getallen 1 t/m 10: </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e083183c04c6a1f064e7f0a5be14e196/02cd5/foldergebaren.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.263803680981596%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mapjes labelen\"\n        title=\"mapjes labelen\"\n        src=\"/static/e083183c04c6a1f064e7f0a5be14e196/a6d36/foldergebaren.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e083183c04c6a1f064e7f0a5be14e196/222b7/foldergebaren.png 163w,\n/static/e083183c04c6a1f064e7f0a5be14e196/ff46a/foldergebaren.png 325w,\n/static/e083183c04c6a1f064e7f0a5be14e196/a6d36/foldergebaren.png 650w,\n/static/e083183c04c6a1f064e7f0a5be14e196/02cd5/foldergebaren.png 821w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Om tenslotte een nieuw gebaar te tonen en het algoritme een voorspelling te laten maken: </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/418746bf5f45691e76c0ab56e1d657c6/29114/sign_lan.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"voorspelling\"\n        title=\"voorspelling\"\n        src=\"/static/418746bf5f45691e76c0ab56e1d657c6/a6d36/sign_lan.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/418746bf5f45691e76c0ab56e1d657c6/222b7/sign_lan.png 163w,\n/static/418746bf5f45691e76c0ab56e1d657c6/ff46a/sign_lan.png 325w,\n/static/418746bf5f45691e76c0ab56e1d657c6/a6d36/sign_lan.png 650w,\n/static/418746bf5f45691e76c0ab56e1d657c6/e548f/sign_lan.png 975w,\n/static/418746bf5f45691e76c0ab56e1d657c6/3c492/sign_lan.png 1300w,\n/static/418746bf5f45691e76c0ab56e1d657c6/29114/sign_lan.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Hear: Een app voor doven?","date":"2018-02-07","category":"Projects"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Hear-Een-app-voor-doven/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3309693220","3318396998","3649515864","63159454"]}